---
title: WJRH
---
<div class="row">
  <div class="twelve columns">
    <video autoplay loop muted>
      <source src="http://wjrh.org.s3.amazonaws.com/fa370c6a168efad0ac71dcc54615567f.ogv"/>
      <source src="http://wjrh.org.s3.amazonaws.com/6a9615f30476f8ef7f3f47d2206e612f.mp4"/>
    </video>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="row main-title">
	<div class="twelve columns">
		<h1>Spring Semester Shows</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="ten columns offset-by-one column">
		<p>The new board has been selected and winter break coming to an end, but it is almost time for Spring shows! Keep an eye on your school emails for the date of the first general body meeting, in which you will be able to register for a time slot for your show. As always, you can keep listening to our pre-recorded shows online:  <%= link_to 'View recorded programs', '/programs' %>.</p>
	</div>
</div>
<div class="row">
    <% @programs.sample(4).each do |program| %>
    <div class="three columns">
    	<a href="/<%=program['shortname']%>"><%= tag :img, :src => program['image'], :style => "width: 100%" %></a>
  		<a href="/<%=program['shortname']%>"><h6><%= program['name'] %></h6></a>
  		</div>
    <% end %>
</div>
